(Printer Not Working) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Keywords: printer not printing printer offline printer error cannot print) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Steps to fix printer issues:) Tj T*
(1. Check printer is powered on and connected \(USB or network\).) Tj T*
(2. Check for paper jams and clear them carefully.) Tj T*
(3. Ensure paper is loaded correctly in the tray.) Tj T*
(4. On your PC: Settings > Printers > right-click printer > Set as Default.) Tj T*
(5. Clear the print queue: Settings > Printers > Open Queue > Cancel All.) Tj T*
(6. Restart the Print Spooler: Services > Print Spooler > Restart.) Tj T*
(7. Reinstall printer driver from manufacturer website.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Network Printer Issues:) Tj T*
(- Ping the printer IP to check connectivity.) Tj T*
(- Re-add the printer using its IP address.) Tj T*
(- Contact IT if printer shows offline on the network.) Tj T*
